name: BCOoLExamples
tagline: The project contains examples of the operators in BCOoL. After compiled, operators can be used to generate the coordination between models. Examples of operators are: synchronized product between Timed Finite State Machine (TFSM), synchronized product between TFSM and Activity diagramas. Please visit  http://timesquare.inria.fr/BCOoL for further information.
body:
# BCOoLExamples
This contains BCOoL examples which includes the specification of a BCOoL operator plus a model. The BCOoL specification can be used to coordinate the example models.
[BCOoL site](http://timesquare.inria.fr/BCOoL)
